OL,5, Pint-sized bottles of still and        
OL,6, sparkling wine are to appear on shelves
OL,7, in the UK, the government has said.    
OL,9,FThe new 568ml size will offer more     
OL,10,Fchoice for customers, according to the 
OL,11,FDepartment for Business and Trade.     
OL,13,FIt also said it will not introduce new 
OL,14,Frules on selling in imperial measures. 
OL,16,FLegislation to be tabled in the new    
OL,17,Fyear will see the pint-sized bottles   
OL,18,Fsold in supermarkets, pubs, clubs and  
OL,19,Frestaurants.                           
